Text: Christ was not a Jew? I love you guys! Please, whatever you're doing, don't stop. But I am pretty sure he was 'cut'. Maybe it means in a metaporical sense? Small nose? Saves, but doesn't invest at 5%? Never once told a joke about 2 men coming out of a bar? Never studied acountancy?
